      <pubtit>Whole-organism mapping of the genetics of gene expression at cellular resolution</pubtit>
      <p><img src="/images/pubpic/sceqtl.png" class="img-responsive" width="33%" style="float: left" /></p>
      <p>We map regulatory variants in C. elegans across the different cell-types, and discover loci that affect individual neurons in a cell-specific manner.</p>
      <p><em>E. Ben-David, J. Boocock, L. Guo, S. Zdraljevic, J. S. Bloom, L. Kruglyak</em></p>
      <p><strong><a href="https://doi.org/10.1101/2020.08.23.263798">bioRxiv (2020)</a></strong></p>
